{"tid":1740862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「好緊要 」大家唔好忘記聽日係咩日子！","createTime":"2019-11-20T05:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T07:13:36.000Z","uid":289694,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ead54653abe276a51a3218395f00e0da899c262b","tid":1740862,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"聽日11月21日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗恐襲四個月呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋呢五個月實在失去太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日要繼續黎明行動，繼續周圍塞，全港人都唔會忘記呢個殺人政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家雖然好累，包括我，但我絕不放棄🔥🔥🔥🔥堅持到勝利既一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快啲同我入嚟推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一日我哋永世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e305e606f757f1ed3